Package ca.openosp.openo.integration.fhir.interfaces

Interface ImmunizationInterface

All Superinterfaces:
Immunization
All Known Implementing Classes:
Prevention
public interface ImmunizationInterface extends Immunization
An interface to be used with any object model that references data for an immunization.

The getImmunizationProperty method can be used in conjunction with the ImmunizationProperty enum to fetch key:value pairs from an entity class.

This interface is currently being used in FHIR mapping.
